public class IdBasedTriplePatternQueryIter
extends Object
implements Iterator<IdBasedBinding>, com.hp.hpl.jena.sparql.core.Closeable

A query iterator that provides ID-based bindings for an ID-based triple pattern which are compatible with the bindings provided by an input operator.

Author:
Olaf Hartig
